{"tid":401562,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人生好似咩都唔岩咁","createTime":"2017-09-15T16:44:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T17:48:15.000Z","uid":10691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b1a9d76166a4256c1a55a821a8dcaff5f75b89cc","tid":401562,"uid":10691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T16:44:53.000Z","msg":"我做影相 做左五年助手 而家出黎做in house 都係得14k 長短週 <br />\n我都諗過轉行 但係諗深一層 我除左影相 真係乜九都唔識 真係可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但影相又冇左個時ge熱誠 識人又唔多 自己開又搵唔到客<br />\n中間做過下pt 廚房 sale 地盤 沖咖啡 樣樣都感覺睇唔到未來 同唔岩自己<br />\n唉<br />\n廿八歲仲好似一事無成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求屌醒<br />\n暫時人生目標想開小食店 儲緊錢<br />\n<br />\n純粹想放下負能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0d537613c0b17d75c1387a6b6b585feb6afbef","tid":401562,"uid":13625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T16:48:59.000Z","msg":"嗯 我喺入黎睇故故嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順便吸收下你啲負能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3538fc536e58fff7286fffbd65d49301d84d297c","tid":401562,"uid":10691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T16:50:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嗯 我喺入黎睇故故嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順便吸收下你啲負能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇咩故睇 都係一個香港典型失敗者寫照<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec0eb6e3469cd01b71dbf0c96a3c96553be4dea","tid":401562,"uid":19900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T16:51:19.000Z","msg":"有冇作品睇吓？<br />\n同埋有咩原因令你失去熱誠？<br />\n我都係想入行嘅人 但仲未起到步 學習中<br />\n而家都係做吓d散工咁"},{"pid":"f8068edc1963f09346fc76745d85be157d9e3f57","tid":401562,"uid":13625,"li